.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-TRANSACTION-LOG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-transaction-log \- print wallet ledger as a text log
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-transaction-log
.RB [ --account
.IR address ]
.RB [ --limit
.IR N ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints ledger entries as tab-separated text lines suitable for piping
to tools like
.BR grep (1)
or
.BR awk (1).
.PP
Output format (tab-separated):
.nf
DATE\tACCOUNT\tDIRECTION\tAMOUNT_SAT\t[NOTE]
.fi
Default limit is 200 entries; use
.B --account
to filter to one account.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-wallet-export-csv (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-backup (1)
